Server Side Public License, v 1

Radiator is licensed under the Server Side Public License, version 1 (SSPL-1.0).

Full text:
https://www.mongodb.com/licensing/server-side-public-license

Summary (non‑authoritative):
- If you offer the Program (modified or not) as a service to third parties,
  you must make the complete Service Source Code publicly available under SSPL.
- SSPL is source‑available and not OSI‑approved.

A commercial license is available for users who cannot publish their changes.
See docs/licensing.md.
